1
00:00:47.125 --> 00:00:52.667
(Shilong, Dongguan)

2
00:01:01.792 --> 00:01:04.208
Unforgettable days

3
00:01:04.250 --> 00:01:08.583
Faded impressions of home

4
00:01:10.125 --> 00:01:13.833
In your diary you said I’m like

5
00:01:13.875 --> 00:01:17.583
an infatuated child, looking at the world

6
00:01:18.417 --> 00:01:21.912
But that sky above the canopy-

7
00:01:21.917 --> 00:01:25.333
wasn’t it the same back then?

8
00:01:25.917 --> 00:01:32.125
That day I didn’t understand your words

9
00:01:36.042 --> 00:01:43.292
Now I continue making a busy life for myself

10
00:01:44.708 --> 00:01:52.292
But I dream of being a simple person again

11
00:01:59.667 --> 00:02:02.250
(Wang Jiamei)

12
00:02:03.333 --> 00:02:05.417
Sis, no more. I’m on a diet

13
00:02:06.417 --> 00:02:07.583
You’re already so thin

14
00:02:07.625 --> 00:02:09.042
and you’re dieting?

15
00:02:09.500 --> 00:02:10.792
Mom, don’t you know?

16
00:02:10.833 --> 00:02:12.792
Jiamei wants to be a model

17
00:02:15.667 --> 00:02:16.833
You...

18
00:02:16.875 --> 00:02:19.662
Don’t speak our dialect with her

19
00:02:19.667 --> 00:02:20.958
Your Cantonese is poor

20
00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.625
Don’t set a bad example for her

21
00:02:22.958 --> 00:02:27.167
How could I?
She already speaks like a Guangdong girl

22
00:03:20.417 --> 00:03:22.542
Wang Jiamei, what did she just do? What happened?

23
00:03:25.417 --> 00:03:26.292
Why didn’t you say anything?

24
00:03:26.333 --> 00:03:27.958
Don’t you know she could die?

25
00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.583
Answer me!

26
00:03:31.583 --> 00:03:34.917
You’d better stop the bleeding,
you said she could die

27
00:03:59.667 --> 00:04:01.167
Are you Wang Jiamei?

28
00:04:01.208 --> 00:04:02.250
Yes

29
00:04:02.875 --> 00:04:03.958
I am Miss Mak

30
00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:05.250
The students all call me Miss Mak

31
00:04:05.292 --> 00:04:06.708
the school social worker

32
00:04:07.167 --> 00:04:08.583
How would you like me to address you?

33
00:04:09.125 --> 00:04:10.458
Do you have an English name?

34
00:04:10.750 --> 00:04:12.917
K-A-M-A, Kama

35
00:04:15.500 --> 00:04:18.375
I know most of the 9th grade students

36
00:04:18.417 --> 00:04:19.917
but I don’t know you

37
00:04:19.958 --> 00:04:21.625
You must be a quiet girl

38
00:04:23.583 --> 00:04:25.120
Although you get good grades

39
00:04:25.125 --> 00:04:28.958
some teachers feel you don’t like them

40
00:04:29.792 --> 00:04:32.417
Actually, I feel that some teachers don’t like me

41
00:04:34.375 --> 00:04:36.625
You wrote on Facebook

42
00:04:37.958 --> 00:04:40.958
I turned on the lights and saw the bed was bloody

43
00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:44.708
The two of us were rolling on the bed

44
00:04:45.292 --> 00:04:46.792
like pigs at a butcher’s

45
00:04:47.292 --> 00:04:49.125
That was my first time

46
00:04:49.750 --> 00:04:52.250
That was my boyfriend in Dongguan

47
00:04:52.292 --> 00:04:53.875
We broke up

48
00:04:54.458 --> 00:04:55.917
Dongguan?

49
00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:58.458
You’ve been in Hong Kong a year now

50
00:04:59.250 --> 00:05:01.625
and you’ve just turned

51
00:05:08.208 --> 00:05:09.917
So can you tell me why

52
00:05:09.958 --> 00:05:12.328
you saw your classmate slit her wrists

53
00:05:12.333 --> 00:05:14.083
but didn’t tell Miss Wu?

54
00:05:17.667 --> 00:05:19.167
Because I was scared

55
00:05:23.375 --> 00:05:25.500
Why did she cut herself with a knife?

56
00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:34.292
Many things are difficult to explain

57
00:05:57.042 --> 00:05:58.708
What is it, Officer Chong?

58
00:06:01.042 --> 00:06:02.875
Did you steal his girlfriend?

59
00:06:02.917 --> 00:06:04.375
How did you know?

60
00:06:04.417 --> 00:06:05.875
I heard the rumors

61
00:06:17.792 --> 00:06:19.375
I hitched a ride

62
00:06:19.417 --> 00:06:20.792
Yiu Tung Street, right?

63
00:06:26.042 --> 00:06:27.375
Let’s go

64
00:06:31.583 --> 00:06:33.417
You forgot your phone

65
00:06:34.875 --> 00:06:36.417
Coming

66
00:08:01.458 --> 00:08:03.708
The last person to see the victim was
Ting Tsz-chung

67
00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:05.833
He hasn’t been home since last night

68
00:08:06.875 --> 00:08:07.708
We’ve found the landlord

69
00:08:07.750 --> 00:08:10.292
CSI has gone over the room with an arc lamp

70
00:08:10.333 --> 00:08:11.667
There are bloodstains all over the floor

71
00:08:19.167 --> 00:08:20.167
Are there any witnesses?

72
00:08:21.333 --> 00:08:22.662
There’s an old lady

73
00:08:22.667 --> 00:08:24.500
Why don’t you rest a bit?

74
00:08:25.167 --> 00:08:26.708
If you think of anything

75
00:08:26.750 --> 00:08:28.875
please let us know, OK?

76
00:08:41.625 --> 00:08:42.708
Mr. Ting

77
00:08:43.042 --> 00:08:44.625
What are you cooking?

78
00:08:44.958 --> 00:08:46.875
Do you need any help?

79
00:09:02.042 --> 00:09:03.333
Please take a picture for me

80
00:09:03.708 --> 00:09:04.833
Of what?

81
00:09:05.208 --> 00:09:06.250
Of me

82
00:09:06.292 --> 00:09:07.292
Of you?

83
00:09:08.125 --> 00:09:09.208
Here, I’ll do it

84
00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.083
OK

85
00:09:22.500 --> 00:09:25.125
(Looking for Mei)

86
00:09:38.875 --> 00:09:40.412
No, no, help me

87
00:09:40.417 --> 00:09:42.750
Help me, help me

88
00:09:45.167 --> 00:09:46.458
What the fuck is it?

89
00:09:46.750 --> 00:09:47.750
Pick up

90
00:09:54.125 --> 00:09:56.000
Stamp the receipt and give it to me

91
00:09:58.417 --> 00:10:02.667
Hurry up! You’re so slow

92
00:10:03.958 --> 00:10:06.542
I need to pee

93
00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:08.833
Pee?

94
00:10:09.667 --> 00:10:11.583
By the time you get to the customer

95
00:10:11.625 --> 00:10:14.500
they’ll complain the meat has gone bad

96
00:10:18.417 --> 00:10:20.542
Move it!

97
00:10:23.458 --> 00:10:24.792
Move it!

98
00:10:27.958 --> 00:10:28.958
Get out of here!

99
00:10:29.000 --> 00:10:30.167
Where are you from?

100
00:10:30.750 --> 00:10:31.917
Huh?

101
00:10:33.542 --> 00:10:35.125
I’m asking where you’re from, damnit

102
00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:47.125
This morning, police found poois of blood

103
00:10:47.167 --> 00:10:50.083
in an apartment in Sham Shui Pa

104
00:10:50.125 --> 00:10:52.958
They believe someone was murdered there

105
00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:55.495
It is thought that the victim was a woman

106
00:10:55.500 --> 00:10:59.042
A male tenant is wanted by the police

107
00:10:59.083 --> 00:11:01.333
He has not been located

108
00:11:01.917 --> 00:11:03.667
Boy-boy no PlayStation

109
00:11:03.708 --> 00:11:05.662
Finish summer homework first

110
00:11:05.667 --> 00:11:06.292
Yes

111
00:11:06.333 --> 00:11:07.625
See you tonight

112
00:11:16.042 --> 00:11:17.042
Not doing anything?

113
00:11:17.083 --> 00:11:18.333
Madam Law

114
00:11:20.167 --> 00:11:21.125
Chong

115
00:11:21.792 --> 00:11:23.083
Do you really have to work so hard?

116
00:11:23.708 --> 00:11:24.500
Huh?

117
00:11:24.542 --> 00:11:26.542
You’ll exhaust yourself

118
00:11:26.583 --> 00:11:28.542
How’s the murder case going?

119
00:11:32.292 --> 00:11:34.037
The victim is Wang Jiamei

120
00:11:34.042 --> 00:11:36.833
age 16, from Hunan

121
00:11:37.792 --> 00:11:40.037
Her mother remarried 7 years ago

122
00:11:40.042 --> 00:11:42.250
but she failed to get a Hong Kong visa

123
00:11:42.292 --> 00:11:44.458
So she moved to Shilong in Dongguan

124
00:11:45.458 --> 00:11:48.370
Since her stepfather’s family was nearby

125
00:11:48.375 --> 00:11:49.958
and it’s close to Hong Kong

126
00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:52.542
so her mother could easily come back to visit

127
00:11:54.417 --> 00:11:55.917
A year ago

128
00:11:55.958 --> 00:11:58.458
she immigrated to Hong Kong

129
00:11:59.125 --> 00:12:01.083
She left school before finishing 9th grade

130
00:12:01.875 --> 00:12:04.583
She supposedly was an assistant
at a modelling company

131
00:12:05.833 --> 00:12:07.500
but actually was a paid escort

132
00:12:08.083 --> 00:12:11.500
She was killed during sex with a client

133
00:12:11.542 --> 00:12:15.125
Her flesh was chopped up
and flushed down the toilet

134
00:12:16.042 --> 00:12:18.042
The killer ripped the skin off her face

135
00:12:19.333 --> 00:12:23.083
and carted her bones to Shek Kip Mei Market

136
00:12:24.375 --> 00:12:27.292
Great! So the case is closed?

137
00:12:31.333 --> 00:12:33.000
The killer, Ting Tsz-chung

138
00:12:33.542 --> 00:12:34.917
age 29

139
00:12:35.958 --> 00:12:38.083
claims to be a delivery driver

140
00:12:38.792 --> 00:12:40.958
but he’s a triad member

141
00:12:41.625 --> 00:12:43.500
Sells smuggled cigarettes

142
00:12:44.625 --> 00:12:47.167
The day of the murder was
the first time he had met her

143
00:12:48.292 --> 00:12:49.542
There were no bad feelings between them

144
00:12:49.583 --> 00:12:52.953
But they may have taken ketamine

145
00:12:52.958 --> 00:12:54.250
before sex

146
00:12:54.833 --> 00:12:57.458
causing him to kill her while under the influence

147
00:13:01.583 --> 00:13:03.458
Don’t smoke in my home

148
00:13:04.875 --> 00:13:06.292
You think cops can do whatever they want?

149
00:13:07.958 --> 00:13:10.083
Always dreaming of being a movie star

150
00:13:10.583 --> 00:13:12.875
or a model

151
00:13:12.917 --> 00:13:14.250
but she never looks in the mirror

152
00:13:14.292 --> 00:13:16.792
She looks just like her rotten dad

153
00:13:16.833 --> 00:13:18.500
Modelling is about more than height

154
00:13:18.833 --> 00:13:20.750
And she goes out with so many guys

155
00:13:21.292 --> 00:13:23.208
She’s always out all night

156
00:13:23.250 --> 00:13:24.708
taking birth control pills

157
00:13:24.750 --> 00:13:26.662
I know she has a boyfriend

158
00:13:26.667 --> 00:13:28.875
Fine! Don’t come back!

159
00:13:29.458 --> 00:13:31.667
Madam, the test results are back

160
00:13:31.708 --> 00:13:34.000
Your daughter may very well have passed away

161
00:13:36.583 --> 00:13:38.875
You mean she’s dead?

162
00:13:40.417 --> 00:13:42.000
What are you saying?

163
00:13:42.042 --> 00:13:42.708
Sir

164
00:13:42.750 --> 00:13:43.583
Dead, dead, dead

165
00:13:43.625 --> 00:13:45.417
Perfect timing

166
00:13:45.458 --> 00:13:46.917
Talk to her

167
00:13:47.833 --> 00:13:48.708
DPC 51334

168
00:13:48.750 --> 00:13:49.750
She’s hostile

169
00:13:49.792 --> 00:13:51.125
and thinks her daughter is still alive

170
00:13:51.167 --> 00:13:52.375
You’re crazy!

171
00:13:52.667 --> 00:13:55.625
Not thinks - hopes

172
00:13:57.792 --> 00:13:59.333
What do you want me to do?

173
00:13:59.375 --> 00:14:01.250
Make her believe her daughter is dead?

174
00:14:08.708 --> 00:14:10.208
Don’t smoke so much

175
00:14:14.625 --> 00:14:16.042
You don’t need to

176
00:14:16.708 --> 00:14:19.375
call Missing Persons every day

177
00:14:20.958 --> 00:14:22.625
They’ve given the case

178
00:14:23.708 --> 00:14:25.792
to us in Regional Crimes

179
00:14:41.917 --> 00:14:43.583
You’re luckier than many others

180
00:14:45.625 --> 00:14:48.917
In Hong Kong, one person goes missing every hour

181
00:14:50.250 --> 00:14:51.708
Many parents

182
00:14:52.792 --> 00:14:53.750
don’t know for years

183
00:14:53.792 --> 00:14:56.292
whether their children are alive or dead

184
00:15:35.083 --> 00:15:36.208
- Hi, Chuen
-May

185
00:15:43.500 --> 00:15:44.625
Chef

186
00:15:44.875 --> 00:15:47.083
It must feel good to take your shirt off, right?

187
00:15:47.125 --> 00:15:48.542
You can, too

188
00:15:49.625 --> 00:15:51.250
Let’s make a date then

189
00:15:55.750 --> 00:15:56.792
Hello, Manager

190
00:15:56.958 --> 00:15:57.583
May

191
00:15:57.625 --> 00:15:59.792
Mr. Ma keeps asking what time you start work

192
00:16:00.125 --> 00:16:02.125
Does he sign my paychecks?

193
00:16:04.833 --> 00:16:06.917
May, you’re finally here!

194
00:16:06.958 --> 00:16:08.250
Let’s dance

195
00:16:08.292 --> 00:16:10.833
No way. I need to make a living

196
00:16:10.875 --> 00:16:12.208
Are you shy?

197
00:16:12.500 --> 00:16:15.792
Well

198
00:16:15.875 --> 00:16:17.750
I’m not shameless

199
00:16:34.500 --> 00:16:38.500
Goodbye, my love

200
00:16:40.500 --> 00:16:46.542
I don’t know when we’ll meet again

201
00:16:46.583 --> 00:16:50.208
I’ve given you everything

202
00:16:50.250 --> 00:16:53.625
Please cherish that

203
00:16:53.667 --> 00:16:58.500
Don’t betray my love

204
00:17:05.083 --> 00:17:06.417
You’re still awake?

205
00:17:07.292 --> 00:17:08.167
How come?

206
00:17:08.542 --> 00:17:10.792
Sisterly bonding?

207
00:17:12.208 --> 00:17:14.083
It’s too hot

208
00:17:14.125 --> 00:17:16.708
Of course, all the lights are on

209
00:17:17.542 --> 00:17:19.000
Uncle can’t sleep with the lights on

210
00:17:25.292 --> 00:17:26.375
Jiamei

211
00:17:27.375 --> 00:17:29.083
The earrings Xia gave us

212
00:17:30.125 --> 00:17:31.917
actually belong to her daughter

213
00:17:31.958 --> 00:17:34.750
She regifted them

214
00:17:35.417 --> 00:17:37.583
She’s so cheap she wants them back?

215
00:17:38.125 --> 00:17:39.542
Why not?

216
00:17:41.708 --> 00:17:44.417
She got you a similar pair

217
00:17:47.500 --> 00:17:48.667
I don’t want them

218
00:17:52.208 --> 00:17:53.750
Then throw them away yourself

219
00:17:56.667 --> 00:17:58.417
Don’t be like that, Jiamei

220
00:17:59.083 --> 00:18:00.042
Come here

221
00:18:00.083 --> 00:18:01.125
What is it?

222
00:18:01.417 --> 00:18:02.917
Stop whining!

223
00:18:04.250 --> 00:18:05.750
What have I done to you?

224
00:18:07.417 --> 00:18:09.000
They don’t belong to us

225
00:18:09.625 --> 00:18:11.458
Who says you’re poor?

226
00:18:12.958 --> 00:18:14.500
I buy you everything you want

227
00:18:15.083 --> 00:18:16.667
You said you wanted to go online

228
00:18:16.708 --> 00:18:18.542
I got you a $3000 computer

229
00:18:19.208 --> 00:18:21.250
You think I have a fortune stashed away?

230
00:18:24.292 --> 00:18:25.625
You can’t stand it anymore?

231
00:18:25.833 --> 00:18:27.120
Fine

232
00:18:27.125 --> 00:18:29.667
I’ll withdraw you from school tomorrow

233
00:18:30.792 --> 00:18:32.917
If you want to be a model

234
00:18:33.125 --> 00:18:35.750
go to work

235
00:18:35.792 --> 00:18:36.667
and make some money

236
00:18:36.708 --> 00:18:37.958
Fine

237
00:18:38.292 --> 00:18:40.708
Stop it, Mom. Go take a bath

238
00:18:52.792 --> 00:18:54.000
Which one are you playing?

239
00:18:54.125 --> 00:18:55.495
Circles

240
00:18:55.500 --> 00:18:56.833
Five Circles?

241
00:18:56.875 --> 00:18:58.542
So bold

242
00:18:59.083 --> 00:19:02.208
Do you know what you’re doing?

243
00:19:03.000 --> 00:19:04.500
Four Bamboos

244
00:19:08.333 --> 00:19:09.667
May

245
00:19:10.583 --> 00:19:11.958
I need to talk to you

246
00:19:13.792 --> 00:19:14.875
Here, take my place

247
00:19:15.375 --> 00:19:16.208
May

248
00:19:16.250 --> 00:19:16.917
What is it?

249
00:19:16.958 --> 00:19:19.333
I gave you a pair of earrings for your birthday

250
00:19:19.375 --> 00:19:21.083
They actually belong to my daughter

251
00:19:21.125 --> 00:19:22.917
She’s been looking for them...

252
00:19:22.958 --> 00:19:24.500
They’re expensive

253
00:19:25.083 --> 00:19:26.958
I gave them to my daughter

254
00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:28.995
You don’t want me to take them back, do you?

255
00:19:29.000 --> 00:19:31.667
I’ve brought you a similar pair

256
00:19:31.708 --> 00:19:33.583
Can you switch them with Jiamei’s?

257
00:19:34.083 --> 00:19:35.417
Fakes?

258
00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:38.537
They’re the same to the kids

259
00:19:38.542 --> 00:19:40.542
Really? Then why do you want to trade?

260
00:19:42.208 --> 00:19:43.708
Are they really expensive?

261
00:19:44.833 --> 00:19:46.542
Over $4000,

262
00:19:47.750 --> 00:19:49.708
Sure... I’ll give them back tomorrow

263
00:20:10.083 --> 00:20:11.250
Fatty

264
00:20:11.667 --> 00:20:12.792
What are you doing here?

265
00:20:12.833 --> 00:20:14.750
I came to see the Regional Crime Unit

266
00:20:15.917 --> 00:20:17.250
Sign in here

267
00:20:18.167 --> 00:20:19.250
OK

268
00:20:24.083 --> 00:20:25.792
Write down why you’re here

269
00:20:25.833 --> 00:20:27.167
I came to turn myself in

270
00:20:27.792 --> 00:20:30.000
Young man, admit your mistakes and change

271
00:20:31.375 --> 00:20:32.745
What did you do?

272
00:20:32.750 --> 00:20:34.250
Assault or theft?

273
00:20:35.125 --> 00:20:36.500
I killed someone

274
00:21:10.125 --> 00:21:12.042
Do you understand the consequences

275
00:21:13.750 --> 00:21:15.125
of what you’ve just said?

276
00:21:17.625 --> 00:21:19.208
You may go to jail for life

277
00:21:21.958 --> 00:21:24.125
I hope you’re sure of what you are saying

278
00:21:25.208 --> 00:21:27.042
I only speak the truth

279
00:21:46.417 --> 00:21:47.625
That’s not him

280
00:21:47.750 --> 00:21:49.167
You don’t need to say who it’s not

281
00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:51.667
Is that him?

282
00:21:52.667 --> 00:21:54.208
Definitely not

283
00:22:05.958 --> 00:22:08.167
That’s him, the one with the owl tattoo

284
00:22:09.458 --> 00:22:10.833
Prodigy Hoi

285
00:22:18.500 --> 00:22:19.708
After him!

286
00:22:21.500 --> 00:22:23.542
What the fuck! This is police business

