01:55:09.167 --> 01:55:11.792
I was just passing and thought I’d stop by

1417
01:55:12.375 --> 01:55:14.042
I never imagined you would visit us

1418
01:55:14.083 --> 01:55:15.333
Please sit

1419
01:55:23.833 --> 01:55:25.250
It’s very tasty

1420
01:55:25.292 --> 01:55:27.458
It’s peanut, black-eyed pea, and chicken’s feet soup

1421
01:55:27.500 --> 01:55:28.375
It’s good for you

1422
01:55:28.417 --> 01:55:30.042
You run around so much

1423
01:55:30.083 --> 01:55:31.500
It will strengthen your legs

1424
01:55:38.875 --> 01:55:42.375
Jiamei has been dead for two years

1425
01:55:44.083 --> 01:55:46.333
Six months after Jiamei died

1426
01:55:46.375 --> 01:55:48.208
Jiali got pregnant

1427
01:55:50.083 --> 01:55:52.203
I don’t know what I did wrong in a previous life

1428
01:55:52.208 --> 01:55:54.167
Both daughters are so immature

1429
01:55:54.208 --> 01:55:56.042
hanging with the wrong crowd

1430
01:55:59.542 --> 01:56:02.208
You have a daughter, don’t you?

1431
01:56:02.375 --> 01:56:03.370
How do you know that?

1432
01:56:03.375 --> 01:56:05.042
I heard from your colleague

1433
01:56:05.083 --> 01:56:06.167
Which colleague?

1434
01:56:06.208 --> 01:56:07.542
The one who smokes a lot

1435
01:56:10.792 --> 01:56:12.542
That’s right, Officer Chong

1436
01:56:13.417 --> 01:56:16.542
Go out with Jiali when you have time

1437
01:56:17.083 --> 01:56:18.245
If she could

1438
01:56:18.250 --> 01:56:19.542
date you

1439
01:56:19.583 --> 01:56:21.250
then I could relax

1440
01:56:24.417 --> 01:56:26.625
See, you’re already making eyes at each other

1441
01:56:27.500 --> 01:56:28.958
Another bowl of soup?

1442
01:56:29.000 --> 01:56:30.917
No, thanks. I’m full

1443
01:56:30.958 --> 01:56:32.583
After this chicken’s foot, I’ll be completely full

1444
01:56:32.625 --> 01:56:33.708
You’re full?

1445
01:56:33.750 --> 01:56:35.042
Good

1446
01:56:35.083 --> 01:56:37.083
Jiali, put the baby down

1447
01:56:37.125 --> 01:56:38.625
Take a walk with Officer Chong

1448
01:56:38.667 --> 01:56:39.708
Go, go

1449
01:56:39.750 --> 01:56:40.833
Another walk?

1450
01:56:40.875 --> 01:56:42.750
I’ve been out all day with

1451
01:56:43.417 --> 01:56:44.583
my daughter and ex-wife

1452
01:56:44.625 --> 01:56:45.792
all day long

1453
01:56:46.583 --> 01:56:47.750
I’m exhausted

1454
01:56:48.583 --> 01:56:49.917
So there’s no chance

1455
01:56:49.958 --> 01:56:51.375
You should have told me sooner

1456
01:56:51.417 --> 01:56:53.583
I just wasted my breath

1457
01:57:06.625 --> 01:57:08.458
You want me to take a picture of you again?

1458
01:57:09.250 --> 01:57:11.333
How about I take one with you?

1459
01:57:46.208 --> 01:57:48.000
I’ve always wanted to ask

1460
01:57:49.583 --> 01:57:51.125
Who is this?

1461
01:57:52.208 --> 01:57:55.208
Actually, we don’t know who she is

1462
01:57:55.917 --> 01:57:57.375
Years ago

1463
01:57:57.417 --> 01:57:59.828
we were shopping in Dongguan

1464
01:57:59.833 --> 01:58:01.625
and saw a photo salon

1465
01:58:02.125 --> 01:58:03.917
The pictures in the window were so nice

1466
01:58:03.958 --> 01:58:05.833
Jiamei wanted a portrait

1467
01:58:05.875 --> 01:58:07.958
but we couldn’t afford it

1468
01:58:08.000 --> 01:58:11.995
We envied her for having such a nice photo

1469
01:58:12.000 --> 01:58:16.000
so we begged the owner to sell us this photo

1470
01:58:16.375 --> 01:58:19.375
The owner thought Jiamei was very strange

1471
01:58:25.208 --> 01:58:26.792
2007

1472
01:58:26.833 --> 01:58:28.042
Smile

1473
01:58:29.667 --> 01:58:30.958
One, two, three

1474
01:58:31.125 --> 01:58:32.208
Again

1475
01:58:33.667 --> 01:58:34.875
Smile

1476
01:58:35.792 --> 01:58:37.042
Smile

1477
01:58:40.375 --> 01:58:46.000
(In memory of Jiamei)

